data.description: Welcome to this unique opportunity!!!! This typical ranch, located on one acre of land, is a recently completed new construction home. Surrounded by nature, but still 25 minutes away from Fort Myers beach, this location allows you to enjoy the best of both worlds. The house offers an open combination of a brand-new kitchen and living room, with a separate dining room area.   All appliances are new. The master bedroom boasts a large walking closet and a master bathroom with dual sinks. The second and third bedroom are equally comfortable with ample built in closets. The spacious laundry room is conveniently located inside of the house. Stepping out you will enjoy a super comfortable under roof, deck ideal for different activities.   If you enjoy nature, this is for you. The big yard is fully fenced, and it offers a great potential for planting trees, grow your favorite plants or raising your own chickens. A huge and sturdy chicken coop is already in place. Coconut and mangoes trees are planted around the property.   Everything in this house is new. Come and check yourself! Don't miss out this opportunity! Seller motivated, bring your offer now before is too late.   Pre approval required for Offer submission.
